config.splatcraft.optimise_desync.toolti:
If the client waits for the server's
confirmation for certain actions,
such as changing squid form.
Only enable if you are experiencing
frequent desync issues.

If view bobbing should be
disabled under certain
conditions.

The radius at which to
render stage blocks.
config.splatcraft.color_lock.tooltip:
When enabled, ink colors are
replaced with just a friendly
or hostile color.
Useful for color-blind users.
config.splatcraft.ink_splash_particle_on:
If ink splash particles are
displayed on entering ink,
movement in ink, or leaving
ink.
config.splatcraft.ink_squid_soul_particl: Ink Squid Soul Particle On Death

If an ink squid soul particle
displays when ink squids or
players die.

Disables smooth biome blending
from Sodium to fix odd ink
blending between blocks.
